divs: Sighting DetailsMy girlfriend and I with our kids were trick or treating. The sky was very clear with only a few stars out. My girlfriend pointed to sky to show me to lights in sky that appeared to be like stars and were very bright and close together. They looked unnatural and we were commenting on that fact when the lower orb faded and disappeared and then the upper one. We were freaked out and kept saying did you just see what I saw and we agreed to very large bright objects just disappeared from sight. crazy
Summary: two lights in sky star like but unnatural looking very bright then one disappeared then other
